Package org.vadere.util.potential.calculators

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EikonalSolver  
    PotentialFieldCalculator
    A PotentialFieldInitializer initializes and updates a given potential field.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfigurationSpacePotentialProvider
    Provides the potential values in a configuration space based on 2D geometry and 1D rotation.
    EikonalSolverFIM
    Implementation of the sequential fast iterative method (FIM) presented in 'A Fast Iterative Method for Eikonal Equations' jeong-2008.
    EikonalSolverFMM
    EikonalSolverFMM initializes a potential field on basis of the fast marching algorithm.
    EikonalSolverFSM
    Implementation of the sequential fast sweeping method (FSM) presented in 'A fast sweeping method for Eikonal equations' zhao-2005.
    PotentialFieldCalculatorAirLine  
    PotentialFieldCalculatorDijkstra  
    PotentialFieldCalculatorFastMarching3D
    Uses the fast-marching algorithm to solve the Eikonal equation (F(x) * |grad phi|=1) in a given 3D room.
    PotentialFieldCalculatorNone
